{"tid":606450,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【世紀對決】羅力威踩上力威健身挑機！！！！（有片多圖）","createTime":"2018-03-26T13:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T11:31:44.000Z","uid":11585,"like":110,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"fabb112407136e50c09fcf11640f35acd998edea","tid":606450,"uid":11585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"創作歌手羅力威即將喺月底同雨僑拉埋天窗，作為「準新郎」，佢當然要保持Fit爆身型啦，所以佢就特地向同樣都叫力威嘅著名健身教練胡力威（胡師傅）請教，希望可以傳授「超濃縮」做Gym心得！ <br />\n<br />\n唔知道係咪兩位都叫力威，佢哋一見面就惜惜相識，握手握到唔捨得放手，之後羅力威就喺胡師傅嘅指導下，進行三組唔同動作，搞到羅力威即時大汗疊細汗。不過唔講唔知，原來胡師傅都有聽開羅力威嘅歌，仲大讚佢首新歌《嫁給我》好冧好好聽！如果想睇到「雙力威」世紀同場，咁就一定要去片啦！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/210834_d1fe576b001306a6939575f438cf2f23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F210834_d1fe576b001306a6939575f438cf2f23.png&h=387a400e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180326/bkn-20180326190045996-0326_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180326%2Fbkn-20180326190045996-0326_00862_001.html&d=RsxxxD658N3gi6tisN0bb26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6266d0a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180326/bkn-20180326190045996-0326_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6a6345d8395f7133141c994ceeca98f86481b04e","tid":606450,"uid":7837,"like":127,"dislike":5,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:12:33.000Z","msg":"借wucfu上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cb842f05bd6ef66517e1c0100fad67a3e2a87c","tid":606450,"uid":170668,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:13:08.000Z","msg":"袋底臥推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255911f093f8c9f022f0145561ffdf34bce0f5ad","tid":606450,"uid":45147,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-2